<i>noun</i>: 함구 [함구], 침묵 [침묵], 정적 [정적], 적막 [정막], 암묵 [암ː묵], 묵언 [무건], 고요 [고요] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>함구 [함구]</dt><br>
<dd>holding one's tongue; zipping one's lips; silence</dd><br>
<dd>입을 다물고, 말하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of keeping one's mouth shut without speaking.</dd><br>
<dt>침묵 [침묵]</dt><br>
<dd>silence</dd><br>
<dd>아무 말 없이 조용히 있음. 또는 그런 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of staying still without saying a word, or such state.</dd><br>
<dt>정적 [정적]</dt><br>
<dd>silence</dd><br>
<dd>쓸쓸한 느낌이 들 정도로 고요하고 조용함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being calm and quiet to the extent that evokes feelings of lonesomeness.</dd><br>
<dt>적막 [정막]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quietness; silence</dd><br>
<dd>아무 소리 없이 조용하고 쓸쓸함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being silent and lonesome with no sound being heard.</dd><br>
<dd>2. forlornness</dd><br>
<dd>의지할 곳 없이 외로움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being lonely with no one to depend on.</dd><br>
<dt>암묵 [암ː묵]</dt><br>
<dd>silence; tacitness</dd><br>
<dd>자기의 생각이나 의견을 겉으로 드러내지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>Not revealing one's thought or opinion.</dd><br>
<dt>묵언 [무건]</dt><br>
<dd>silence; muteness</dd><br>
<dd>아무 말도 하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saying nothing.</dd><br>
<dt>고요 [고요]</dt><br>
<dd>silence; quiet; stillness</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽거나 어지럽지 않고 조용한 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being quiet, neither noisy nor chaotic.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>